			<p style=3D"margin-bottom: 15px;">Killing animals to train surgeons is n=
ot only cruel, but also harmful to people as well=E2=80=94<em>a 2020 U.S. m=
ilitary study found that trainees using advanced surgical simulators showed=
 significant improvements in both response times and reduced medical errors=
</em>.</p>

			<p style=3D"margin-bottom: 15px;">Today, 80% of surveyed general surgery=
 programs in the U.S. and Canada=E2=80=94including Harvard, Stanford, and t=
he Cleveland Clinic=E2=80=94use only superior, human-based training methods=
